{
  "stem": "27390.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, everybody had a ration card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first thing, what they did is, if somebody was on the list to be deported, they took away his ration card.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the person had no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even if somebody shared a bit of food, what they had, it didn't help, because the police were-- used to make raids in the middle of-- the Jewish police used to raid, in the middle of the night, and get these people out, if-- wherever they hid.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't hide for long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this went on for a few months until it was in July, 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working in the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I told you before, opposite was this hospital, was a large Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it had a few hundred inmates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, lorries drove up, and they rushed into-- the German Gestapo, SS, and with Jewish police, as well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They rushed in, into that hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the windows were opened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started throwing out these people, from the beds, onto lorries that were standing downstairs, from the third or fourth floor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That building had about four floors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a big building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started throwing, like sacks of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've never-- I will never forget this sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In my life, I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were showing them onto these lorries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people heard about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People that had children or relatives in this hospital came running toward the hospital to try to get them out, before they're being thrown out onto these lorries.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the police were pushing them away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans started shooting, first in the air, then they started shooting into the crowd.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And till finally, this hospital was emptied of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
